    <string name="find_my_phone_title">Find my phone</string>
    <string name="find_my_phone_description">Make your phone ring, even if it\'s on silent, when a preconfigured number calls repeatedly.\n\nThis is not a call blocking feature, but it can block calls.\n\nIt works as follows: when you receive a call from one of the preconfigured phone numbers, the call will either ring normally or be blocked according to your configured rules. However, if the conditions defined below (number of calls and the time interval between them) are met, the call will be automatically rejected and your phone will ring loudly.\n\nA new call from an authorized number will cancel the function.</string>
